data.description: Welcome to your new three-level townhome! This spacious home boasts plenty of living space with three levels of comfortable and convenient living. On the first level, you'll find a spare room, perfect for a home office or guest bedroom, as well as a half bath, laundry room and access to the garage. The second level is the hub of this lovely home, featuring an open kitchen, living room, and dining room. The bright and airy space is perfect for entertaining, and with two additional bedrooms and a full bath on this level, you'll have plenty of room for family members or guests. Finally, the third level features a primary bedroom with a full bath, dual vanity, and walk-in closet. You'll love having a private space to relax and unwind after a long day. Recent updates are air conditioning system, hot water heater, microwave, vinyl plank flooring on second level. Close proximity to shopping, restaurants and military bases.
